Package: dawaR
Title: An API Wrapper Package for DAWA - the Danish Address Web API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Aleksander", "Bang-Larsen", , "contact@aleksanderbl.dk",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-7984-4650"))
Description: This package provides functions to interact with all sections of
    the official Danish Address Web API (also known as DAWA). The development
    of this package is completely independent from the [government entity that maintains the API](sdfi.dk).
